body:
Top Ten Spooky Week Videos!

Another Halloween and another Spooky Week completed! So what are the ten best? Please remember this is just my opinion, you are allowed to have a different one!

10) Outlast 2

I love when they play actually scary games. I love how scared they both get and seeing Dan make dumb decisions that in real life would get him killed. This video is sweet and cute, but they have played much scarier games than this

9) Spooky Golf

I love this video a lot, but I love all of the golf videos a lot! I think that they’re both really cute and competitive and them scaring each other throughout the video was a cute touch. A great video!

8) The Watson-Scott Personality Test

I didn’t like this video as much as everyone else, but there were some sweet moments, like Dan checking if Phil wants to see if the door was unlocked cause the test was making him nervous and Dan telling his story about the snails. There were a lot of little, cute moments but overall the game itself bored me since it got a little predictable the further in they got

7) Swamp Simulator

This video really made me soft for them. Listen, this game was funny not scary at all so watching them actually jump and get scared but simultaneously make fun of it was hilarious. Also, it included the Dan trying told hold Phil’s hand cause he was so scared and Phil teasing him for it

6) Spongebob Slenderpants

Dan and Phil in onesie pajamas while playing a Slender game Sign me the fuck up! This video is so soft with them in their onesies and getting scared it’s all just very adorable!

5) Resident Evil 7

Oh Dan oh poor, sweet Dan. He really was actually so terrified while playing this game and it’s so cute! This game is genuinely horrifying to be fair and the end when Phil put on the mask and scared Dan so bad he fell off the chair? Iconic

4) Friday The 13th

I don’t know why I love this video as much as I do. It’s not as iconic as some of the other ones on this list, there really aren’t too many cute and coupley moments between them in this video, aside from Dan telling Phil to turn the lights back on cause he’s scared and Phil listening cause he doesn’t want Dan to be really scared, and the game itself isn’t as good as some of the other ones. But something about this video just makes me feel warm and I love it a lot

3) Can Your Pet

This video will never not be funny. Phil is so evil in this and Dan is so adorably oblivious up until he sees the bird he cares about so much get destroyed. And Dan’s reaction to it? Iconic. Phil teasing him the whole video and looking smug and evil? Iconic. Dan putting his head on Phil’s shoulder at the end when he’s sad about the game? THE MOST ICONIC

2) The Evil Within 2

Maybe there’s just something wrong with me, but this game did scare me more than Resident Evil 7. And they were very sweet and cute during this video like how Dan got really scared and Phil said in a calming and loving tone, “We’ll just poke our noses in, it’s alright.” Like okay. And Dan wearing Phil’s sweater and them not giving a reason for it aka it’s normal for Dan to wear Phil’s clothes? Ugh my heart!

1) Jumpscare Showdown

Can anyone really argue with this? Dan and Phil doing nothing but trying to scare each other for seventeen minutes is the best Spooky Week will probably ever get honestly
